### Create Drone
POST http://localhost:3000/api/drones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serialNumber": "SKY-AB12-CD34",
  "model": "PHANTOM_4"
}

### Create Drone (Matrice 300)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/drones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serialNumber": "SKY-XY99-ZW01",
  "model": "MATRICE_300"
}

### Create Drone (Mavic 3 Enterprise)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/drones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serialNumber": "SKY-MV3E-0001",
  "model": "MAVIC_3_ENTERPRISE"
}

### List Drones (paginated)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/drones?page=1&limit=10

### List Drones (filter by status)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/drones?status=AVAILABLE

### List Drones (filter by model)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/drones?model=PHANTOM_4

### Get Drone by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/drones/{{droneId}}

### Update Drone
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/drones/{{droneId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "MATRICE_300"
}

### Retire Drone
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/drones/{{droneId}}/retire

### Delete Drone
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/drones/{{droneId}}

### --- Validation Error Cases ---

### Invalid Serial Number (should fail 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/drones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serialNumber": "INVALID",
  "model": "PHANTOM_4"
}

### Invalid Model (should fail 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/drones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serialNumber": "SKY-TE5T-0001",
  "model": "UNKNOWN_MODEL"
}

### Missing Fields (should fail 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/drones
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Unknown Fields (should fail 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/drones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serialNumber": "SKY-TE5T-0002",
  "model": "PHANTOM_4",
  "unknownField": "value"
}

### Duplicate Serial Number (should fail 409 — run Create Drone first)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/drones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serialNumber": "SKY-AB12-CD34",
  "model": "MATRICE_300"
}

### Get Non-existent Drone (should fail 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/drones/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
